FBIS4-7606 "dreeu064_i_94013" FBIS-EEU-94-064 Daily Report 4 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA `Karadzic's Terrorists' Continue Bihac Attack `Karadzic's Terrorists' Continue Bihac Attack AU0404090294 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in Serbo-Croatian 0800 GMT 4 Apr 94 AU0404090294 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Report by Mirza Saikovic] [Excerpts] The Serbian aggressor is continuing his offensive on the Bihac region on this 57th day of fighting in this part of Bosnia-Herzegovina. Karadzic's terrorists last night continued artillery attacks on Bihac and the surrounding area. Civilians in this UN protected zone are still being targeted. [passage omitted] The lines of separation with the paramilitary formations of the so-called Cazin autonomous region were not quiet either. The separatists are constantly opening small-arms fire and provoking clashes. They are still shelling the (?Prusce) area in the Cazin municipality.
